title: Death. Taxes. Excuses.
description: Katie, Ashley and Jay are back with all of the sports? They start by picking desert island athletes then dive into the NFL playoffs, like the Bang Bang Niner Gang (27:22), the Seahawks (29:27), and the end of the Ravens run (37:28). They then talk Luke Kuechly (1:00:59), a Bachelor Update (1:20:45), sign stealing in MLB (1:38:00), and the erotic news of the week (2:04:50). They then finish up with some rhymes (2:12:16).
